Global SaaS Learning Platform (Web + Mobile)

Users hit the platform through CDN and DNS, traffic is protected by WAF and routed via load balancers to API Gateway.
Authentication and IAM secure access.
Compute is handled by a mix of VMs, serverless, and Kubernetes, backed by relational, NoSQL, cache, and object storage.
Async workflows use queues, events, and streaming.
Analytics data flows into a warehouse, feeding ML models for personalization.
Everything is observable, secure, automated via CI/CD and IaC, and protected by backup and DR.


Features:
  Millions of users globally
  Secure login
  Real-time APIs
  Asynchronous processing
  Analytics & ML recommendations
  Multi-region, highly available
  CI/CD, monitoring, security, backups


High-Level Architecture (Logical View)
  Flow (left → right):
  Users → Edge → Network → Compute → Data → Async → Analytics → ML → Ops





